SQLAction

SQLServerProcedureAction
public class ProcedureAction
extends BaseSQLAction

A SQLAction that runs a stored procedure. Note that ProcedureAction has internal state and is not thread-safe.

Since:
1.2
Author:
Andrus Adamchik
